                <h2>The Online Education</h2>
                <p>
                    Online learning involves courses offered by primary institutions that are 100%
                    virtual. Online learning, or virtual classes offered over the internet, is
                    contrasted with traditional courses taken in a brick-and-mortar school building.
                    It is a development in distance education that expanded in the 1990s with the
                    spread of the commercial Internet and the World Wide Web.
                </p>
