                <h2>Learning Management System (LMS)</h2>
                <p>
                    Most online learning occurs through a college's or university's learning
                    management system (LMS). A LMS is a software application for maintaining,
                    delivering, and tracking educational resources. According to the Educause Center
                    for Analysis and Research (ECAR) use of a LMS is nearly ubiquitous as 99% of
                    colleges and universities report having one in place.
                </p>
